		|  Flag Name   |  Value	| Interpretation                      |
		+--------------+--------+-------------------------------------+
		| ACC_VOLATILE | 0x0040	| Declared volatile; cannot be cached.|
		+--------------+--------+-------------------------------------+
		|ACC_TRANSIENT | 0x0080	| Declared transient; not written or  |
		|              |        | read by a persistent object manager.|
		+--------------+--------+-------------------------------------+


